transcription.text:
Speaker 1: Thanks for calling Vasozyte. This is John. How can I help you?

Speaker 2: Yes, I'd like to place an order.

Speaker 1: Okay. Give me a second, please.

Speaker 2: Sure.

Speaker 1: Phone numbers pulling up John Bondy in Youngstown?

Speaker 2: Yep, that's it. You got it.

Speaker 1: Okay. Were you calling to order the Vasozyte?

Speaker 2: Yes.

Speaker 1: Okay. And how many were you looking to get? I see the last time you did three bottles.

Speaker 2: Yeah, I see you got buy three, get three for $1.50.

Speaker 1: Okay. If you see that, I'll honor it. I haven't seen that pop up, but I believe you, so I'll do that for you.

Speaker 2: Yeah, buy three, get three free, $1.49.95.

Speaker 1: Okay. And then it's still going to the Yorktown Lane address?

Speaker 2: Exactly. Everything is exactly the same.

Speaker 1: Okay. Same cart too. Great. I'll let you know when it goes through. One second.

Speaker 2: Okay.

Speaker 1: We're all set, John. You're going to get your buy three, get three, so it'll be six bottles.

Speaker 2: Okay. Sounds cool.

Speaker 1: Thanks.

Speaker 2: Thank you very much.

Speaker 1: Bye-bye.

Speaker 2: Have a great day. Bye.

Speaker 1: You too.
